<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4396876>
    dc:description "FIGURES 93–98. Micropsectra contracta-type: 93—head capsule (arrow indicates spur). Micropsectra insignilobus-type: 94—head capsule. Micropsectra junci-type: 95—head capsule. M. junci-type: 96—mentum (arrow indicates shorter first pair of laterals). Micropsectra radialis-type: 97—head capsule. Micropsectra type A: 98—head capsule (arrow indicates greatly enlarged and convex occipital plate)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4396876/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

